WEBVTT

05:30.456 --> 05:32.416
Excuse me...

05:33.792 --> 05:35.335
Go away.

05:35.377 --> 05:37.337
I'm very sorry.

05:41.508 --> 05:42.885
Our orders.

05:42.926 --> 05:45.012
"A lighter touch..."

09:06.380 --> 09:08.173
Chief Inspector.

09:08.215 --> 09:09.299
What do you have?

09:09.341 --> 09:10.425
We recovered this weapon.

09:22.854 --> 09:23.939
It will be untraceable.

09:23.981 --> 09:26.441
No serial number,
no fingerprints.

09:26.483 --> 09:28.568
Also reports of a gaijin
in the vicinity.

09:28.610 --> 09:32.364
White male, 25 to 30, slender.

09:32.406 --> 09:33.657
Work up a sketch.

11:34.486 --> 11:36.780
Are you okay?

26:28.587 --> 26:31.215
Excuse me.

26:31.257 --> 26:32.508
Thank you.

26:32.550 --> 26:34.677
You're welcome.

28:08.854 --> 28:11.482
Thank you.

28:11.524 --> 28:13.317
I will treasure it.

28:17.905 --> 28:19.281
I am glad.

31:55.581 --> 31:58.208
What troubles you, Kotomichi?

32:11.096 --> 32:13.932
Yes, sir.

47:40.233 --> 47:42.151
Surrender! Don't move!

47:43.945 --> 47:46.948
-You're the criminal priest
Hagan. -(panting)
